member.returns:
Sequence of the similar (duplicate) objects in the local system: 
            A single entry if the object already exists locally but is not mapped to its external counterpart in the connector;
            Null if no duplicates are found.

Sequence of the similar (duplicate) objects in the external system:
            A single entry if the object already exists externally but is not mapped to its local counterpart in the connector;
            Null if no duplicates are found.
